Package: sfe
Version: @VERSION@
Section: editors
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: changfengpro <2728019272@qq.com>
Depends: python3, python3:any
Homepage: https://github.com/changfengpro/SSH-file-editor
Description: SSH-friendly terminal C code editor
 sfe is a lightweight terminal editor for SSH sessions.
 It keeps common Vim-style save and quit commands, and adds
 C syntax highlighting plus VS Code-like completion behavior.
